    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/9",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">basket associated with each stock. If we assume that these weights are approximately constant which is reasonable, it follows that the volatility of the basket and the volatilities of the stocks satisfy the relation</p>",
      "page": 187,
      "polygon": [
        [
          301.203125,
          71.2027833001988
        ],
        [
          513.3164556962025,
          71.2027833001988
        ],
        [
          513.3164556962025,
          116.063720703125
        ],
        [
          301.203125,
          116.063720703125
        ]
