    {
      "id": "/page/0/TextInlineMath/15",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">For example, if the average implied volatility for the components of the QQQQ for the December atthe-money options is 25% and the corresponding QQQQ option is trading at an implied volatility of 19%, the implied correlation is <math display=\"inline\">\\rho \\approx (19/25)^2 = 58\\%</math>.</p>",
      "page": 187,
      "polygon": [
